{
  "text": "Due to the huge amount of data collected in the GC \u00d7 GC-TOFMS data sets for the 20 lettuce samples, a data segmentation and compression strategy based on the use of wavelets [CITATION_1] 87 , especially in the time direction, was proposed to make their chemometric analysis more feasible and reduce computer storage requirements. To this end, GC \u00d7 GC-TOFMS data for the 20 samples were segmented into four parts (A-D) by visual inspection of the chromatograms (Fig. S4) . The bleeding part of the chromatogram was excluded from the data.",
